# 🔍 Vulnerability Scanning & Reporting

## 📌 Project Overview
This project demonstrates **network vulnerability scanning** using Nmap & Nessus.  
The goal is to identify vulnerabilities before attackers can exploit them.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Nmap – Network discovery & port scanning  
- Nessus – Vulnerability assessment  
- Python/Bash – Automation & report formatting  

---

## ⚡ How It Works
1. Run Nmap scan:
```bash
nmap -sV -oN sample_scan.nmap 192.168.1.0/24
